headline: Square Helps UK Retail and Hospitality Businesses Prepare for Black ‘Dine’day Weekend as Consumers Combine Shopping with Eating Out
summary: LONDON, November 04, 2025--As retailers and hospitality businesses gear up for the year’s biggest shopping and dining weekend, Square is helping UK sellers prepare for success with insights from last year’s record-breaking Black Friday and Cyber Monday weekend, and an exclusive offer of up to 50% off Square hardware for a five-week period.
